## 6. File Map (~12 files)

### Demo files (in `public/demos/edtech-school-connect-web-portal/`)
1. `index.html` -- app shell, loads fonts, Chart.js CDN, CSS, JS modules
2. `styles.css` -- full design system (tokens, layout, components)
3. `app.js` -- router, auth state, polling manager, view orchestrator
4. `api.js` -- all fetch calls to `/api/edtech/...` with JWT header injection
5. `login.js` -- dual-role login tiles, form, auth flow
6. `parent-home.js` -- parent overview dashboard (quick stats cards)
7. `teacher-home.js` -- teacher overview dashboard (student card, quick actions)
8. `messages.js` -- shared messaging module (renders correctly for either role)
9. `performance.js` -- gradebook cards + Chart.js radar chart + grade edit (teacher)
10. `activities.js` -- feed renderer + compose form (teacher only)

### Backend files (in `mw-backend/`)
11. `edtech_blueprint.py` -- all `/api/edtech/...` routes: login, messages, performance, activities, seed

### Site registry (in `michaelwegter.com/src/data/`)
12. `workSamples.js` -- add entry for this demo (new file or update if it exists)

**Total: 12 files.** Within cap.

