## 9. Demo Flow for Reviewer (the intended walkthrough)

1. Open `/demos/edtech-school-connect-web-portal/` -- see login page with two tiles
2. Click "Log in as Teacher" -- pre-fills teacher@demo.edu / TeachDemo1
3. See teacher home: Alex Johnson's card, quick actions
4. Go to Performance: see grade cards, update Science from A- to A (save), see confirmation toast
5. Go to Activities: post a new announcement "Science Fair this Friday!"
6. Click logout
7. Click "Log in as Parent" -- pre-fills parent@demo.edu / ParentDemo1
8. See parent home: GPA card reflects updated Science grade (A now), unread message badge
9. Go to Messages: see thread with Mrs. Rivera, reply with a new message
10. Go to Activities: see the Science Fair announcement just posted
11. Go to Performance: see updated Science grade and the "Recent Updates" feed item
12. (Optional) Open second browser tab as teacher, send a reply to the parent message, watch it appear on the parent tab within 4 seconds

